room_title: Escape room "Captain's Curse" by Extreme Escape Redding in Redding
room_description: Captain's Curse is a tale that takes place on a pirate ship. Your Captain has gone rouge and you are tired of living under his orders. He has managed to narrowly escape death while forcing your crew to sail in some of the most dangerous storms all for the sake of finding the bloody treasure. You hatch a plan to escape while docked on dry land, but the Captain will return and if he finds you trying to abandon his ship he will behead you.  Does your crew have what it takes to escape the CAPTAINS CURSE?
